com.continuent.tungsten.fsm.event
Class EventRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.continuent.tungsten.fsm.event.EventRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.util.concurrent.Future<EventStatus>
public class EventRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Future<EventStatus>

Defines an event request, which contains the event to be processed as well as the status of it. This class implements the Future interface so that it can be returned to clients that track status of events.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Robert Hodges
